item.title: Le Brass
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Their homeware products are committed to make a statement for trend followers, interior home design enthusiast, fashionistas and anyone who pursues extraordinary. Every Le Brass product carries this concept in mind and was conveyed by utilising metallic materials such as brass and copper.     We have been inspired by the Australian Lifestyle: Nature, relax & paradise beaches, combined with luxury textures as bronze and marble
